31
00:02:51,244 --> 00:02:52,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It really was.</b></font>

32
00:02:52,514 --> 00:02:56,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They were a terrible bunch,
