34
00:03:00,524 --> 00:03:04,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But I never thought someone would
attack us during our practice run.</b></font>

35
00:03:05,964 --> 00:03:08,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It made me think we can
never let our guard down...</b></font>

36
00:03:08,804 --> 00:03:11,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But you keep on winning!</b></font>

37
00:03:11,034 --> 00:03:15,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've started to feel kinda like,
"Of course Takumi's gonna win!"</b></font>

38
00:03:15,274 --> 00:03:18,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Recently, he's lost a lot of
that newbie shine, huh?</b></font>

39
00:03:18,974 --> 00:03:24,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah, but the fact he's kept winning since
his first race has to weigh pretty heavy.</b></font>

40
00:03:24,954 --> 00:03:26,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's a lot of pressure.</b></font>

41
00:03:26,784 --> 00:03:33,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>With this latest race, I really thought
that Keisuke is an amazing person.</b></font>

42
00:03:33,594 --> 00:03:36,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He refuses to give up, or...</b></font>

43
00:03:36,324 --> 00:03:38,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No matter how impossible the situation seems,</b></font>

44
00:03:38,494 --> 00:03:42,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>for him, the only thing to do is race.</b></font>

45
00:03:42,004 --> 00:03:46,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>His tenacity ended up saving a
race everyone thought we'd lost.</b></font>

46
00:03:46,934 --> 00:03:51,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He pulls everyone around him
into action, making them energized.</b></font>

47
00:03:51,844 --> 00:03:56,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>When I see that, I know I have
to work hard to keep up.</b></font>

48
00:03:56,084 --> 00:03:58,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's so much pressure...</b></font>

49
00:04:00,454 --> 00:04:06,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah, I guess so. I mean, you've made
it this far without having lost once.</b></font>

50
00:04:06,294 --> 00:04:09,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That must be a heavy burden on you drivers.</b></font>

51
00:04:09,424 --> 00:04:11,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We can't even imagine it, huh?</b></font>

52
00:04:11,864 --> 00:04:14,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah... "We"?!</b></font>

53
00:04:37,324 --> 00:04:39,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey. Been waiting long?</b></font>

54
00:04:39,054 --> 00:04:42,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No. What's with this FC?</b></font>

55
00:04:42,664 --> 00:04:47,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's my brother's car. He almost
never lets me borrow it, but...</b></font>

56
00:04:47,534 --> 00:04:51,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I forced him to let me. Anyway, get in!</b></font>

57
00:04:51,634 --> 00:04:53,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay!</b></font>

58
00:05:08,324 --> 00:05:13,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Act 18: Last Drive"</b></font>

59
00:05:17,094 --> 00:05:18,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What do you wanna eat?</b></font>

60
00:05:18,664 --> 00:05:21,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is to thank you for before,
so whatever you want is on me.</b></font>

61
00:05:21,564 --> 00:05:25,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You wanna take the Kan-Etsu
Expressway into Tokyo?</b></font>

62
00:05:25,604 --> 00:05:32,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We could do that, but I don't
like places that are too busy.</b></font>

63
00:05:32,244 --> 00:05:35,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If possible, I'd prefer Gunma to Tokyo.</b></font>

64
00:05:35,744 --> 00:05:38,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're okay with that?</b></font>

65
00:05:38,014 --> 00:05:40,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sure! After all, you have this car,</b></font>

66
00:05:40,584 --> 00:05:43,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>so rather than the big city with all the traffic,</b></font>

67
00:05:43,054 --> 00:05:46,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>it'd be better to go somewhere
we can have a relaxing drive.</b></font>

68
00:05:46,954 --> 00:05:48,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay.</b></font>

69
00:05:54,034 --> 00:05:59,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Wow, what an incredible view!
The cars look like ants!</b></font>

70
00:05:59,604 --> 00:06:02,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I wonder which way the Kan-Etsu is...</b></font>

71
00:06:07,144 --> 00:06:13,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Project D is done going to Saitama, right?
Where will you be heading to next?</b></font>

72
00:06:13,254 --> 00:06:16,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Ibaraki.
--Wow, you're going far!</b></font>

73
00:06:25,794 --> 00:06:29,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I... It's okay, right?</b></font>

74
00:06:29,634 --> 00:06:34,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can keep going to support
you at your races, right?</b></font>

75
00:06:34,234 --> 00:06:39,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You can ignore me if you want.
I won't get in the way.</b></font>

76
00:06:39,274 --> 00:06:43,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I just want to watch! And...</b></font>

77
00:06:43,614 --> 00:06:50,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>And I could be helpful like
last time, even if it was a fluke...</b></font>

78
00:06:53,454 --> 00:06:55,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I swear, you...</b></font>

79
00:06:55,764 --> 00:07:00,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How can I put this? I don't know
if it's youth or innocence, but...</b></font>

80
00:07:00,494 --> 00:07:04,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Once you've decided something,
there's no changing it, is there?</b></font>

81
00:07:06,274 --> 00:07:08,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're the type that can take
corners without hesitation,</b></font>

82
00:07:08,974 --> 00:07:13,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>not even knowing what lies ahead.</b></font>

83
00:07:13,614 --> 00:07:14,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So the answer's "no"?</b></font>

84
00:07:14,774 --> 00:07:19,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Enough about this. Let's talk after we eat.</b></font>

85
00:07:19,854 --> 00:07:22,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't know about you, but I'm hungry.</b></font>

86
00:07:25,554 --> 00:07:29,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hello, Ryosuke? It's me.</b></font>

87
00:07:29,964 --> 00:07:34,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We have an idea of how to address
all the FD's planned repairs.</b></font>

88
00:07:34,034 --> 00:07:37,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I thought I'd let you know.</b></font>

89
00:07:37,204 --> 00:07:41,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I see. Sorry for asking so much, Fumihiro.</b></font>

90
00:07:41,534 --> 00:07:44,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No, no. Nothing of the sort.</b></font>

91
00:07:44,804 --> 00:07:48,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This will result in a dramatic boost
of the FD's racing capabilities.</b></font>

92
00:07:48,644 --> 00:07:51,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is going to be a complete overhaul.</b></font>

93
00:07:51,684 --> 00:07:56,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yes. Going forward, we will
face a string of difficult races.</b></font>

94
00:07:56,524 --> 00:08:00,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We have to make the burden on
the driver even a little lighter.</b></font>

95
00:08:00,754 --> 00:08:05,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay. Tomorrow, Kenta and I will go
scout out the next course as planned.</b></font>

96
00:08:05,894 --> 00:08:08,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Understood. Be careful, and come back safely.</b></font>

97
00:08:08,604 --> 00:08:10,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay.</b></font>

98
00:08:24,244 --> 00:08:26,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It doesn't seem real.</i></b></font>

99
00:08:26,684 --> 00:08:33,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>If someone we didn't know saw us, I bet</i>
<i>we'd look like a couple out on a date.</i></b></font>

100
00:08:33,224 --> 00:08:37,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I've never known such happiness.</i></b></font>

101
00:08:37,264 --> 00:08:41,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It's like being a rotary engine that</i>
<i>can keep running in the red zone!</i></b></font>

102
00:08:41,934 --> 00:08:46,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>So this is the feeling of the person</i>
<i>you like being right next to you.</i></b></font>

103
00:08:46,804 --> 00:08:51,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I don't want to ruin this. It's my first true love!</i></b></font>

104
00:08:59,054 --> 00:09:03,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Incredible... Being on the roads of Akagi</i>
<i>in my darling's passenger seat!</i></b></font>

105
00:09:03,754 --> 00:09:06,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Even though he's running at a</i>
<i>slow pace, I can tell the difference.</i></b></font>

106
00:09:06,554 --> 00:09:08,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It's ultra smooth...</i></b></font>

107
00:09:08,124 --> 00:09:10,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Everything about him is on a different level!</i></b></font>

108
00:09:16,404 --> 00:09:23,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>This is incredible, too! When he shifts up,</i>
<i>you don't feel the change in G forces.</i></b></font>

109
00:09:23,504 --> 00:09:25,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I've never seen anyone per form</i>
<i>such delicate clutchwork</i></b></font>

110
00:09:25,614 --> 00:09:30,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>while driving on a winding road!</i></b></font>

111
00:09:30,684 --> 00:09:34,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>This is what it's like to achieve</i>
<i>near mastery of driving techniques?</i></b></font>

112
00:09:42,024 --> 00:09:45,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Your driving sure is incredible.</b></font>

113
00:09:45,864 --> 00:09:49,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You think? It's not like I was really going at it.</b></font>

114
00:09:49,134 --> 00:09:51,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Maybe that's what made it easier to tell.</b></font>

115
00:09:51,974 --> 00:09:53,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You were completely at ease,</b></font>

116
00:09:53,704 --> 00:09:57,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>almost considerate toward
the clutch and gearbox.</b></font>

117
00:09:57,704 --> 00:10:00,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's not as if I'm always like that.</b></font>

118
00:10:00,174 --> 00:10:06,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>When I get serious and go on the offensive,
I can get sloppy, kick the clutch around...</b></font>

119
00:10:06,014 --> 00:10:12,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Being out on the road and pushing our cars
to their limits puts a lot of stress on them.</b></font>

120
00:10:12,054 --> 00:10:16,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's why when driving normally, I've gotten
in the habit of treating them with more care.</b></font>

121
00:10:16,664 --> 00:10:18,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Huh?</b></font>

122
00:10:18,564 --> 00:10:20,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh, it's Keisuke!</b></font>

123
00:10:20,634 --> 00:10:24,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is unusual. He's brought a girl!</b></font>

124
00:10:24,204 --> 00:10:25,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Who's that? Your girlfriend?</b></font>

125
00:10:25,974 --> 00:10:30,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Shut yer hole! Where do you get off?
Get the hell out of here! Get goin'!</b></font>

126
00:10:35,214 --> 00:10:36,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Jeez!</b></font>

127
00:10:41,054 --> 00:10:47,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Up until I got my 4WD license,
I hung out with a pretty bad crowd.</b></font>

128
00:10:47,194 --> 00:10:53,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I got into a lot of fights, rebelled against
my parents... I caused a lot of problems.</b></font>

129
00:10:53,364 --> 00:10:59,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Looking back, I was just being an idiot.
But at the time, I didn't have any goals,</b></font>

130
00:10:59,834 --> 00:11:03,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and every day I was bored and angry.</b></font>

131
00:11:03,574 --> 00:11:07,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I understand. I know that feeling.</i></b></font>

132
00:11:07,274 --> 00:11:14,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>My parents gave up on me, but my brother
was the only one who knew how I felt.</b></font>

133
00:11:14,884 --> 00:11:16,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Even now I can't forget...</b></font>

134
00:11:16,884 --> 00:11:21,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That time, he took me in
this FC to Mount Akagi.</b></font>

135
00:11:24,764 --> 00:11:27,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Suddenly, he opened her up
full-throttle on the downhill.</b></font>

136
00:11:27,894 --> 00:11:32,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It was such a shock. I really
thought we were done for!</b></font>

137
00:11:32,774 --> 00:11:38,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I totally thought he was taking his no-good
younger brother with him, killing us both.</b></font>

138
00:11:42,314 --> 00:11:44,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's been three years since then.</b></font>

139
00:11:44,784 --> 00:11:48,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I still don't think I've beaten the downhill
my brother showed me that day.</b></font>

140
00:11:48,754 --> 00:11:54,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Huh?! You're joking, right?
Is your brother that good?</b></font>

141
00:11:54,124 --> 00:11:55,624
