00:22:56,784 --> 00:22:59,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll bet more and more races on cornering!</b></font>

286
00:22:59,824 --> 00:23:01,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The timing couldn't be better, eh?</b></font>

287
00:23:01,894 --> 00:23:06,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>According to Ryosuke, your next
opponent will be your toughest one yet.</b></font>

288
00:23:06,094 --> 00:23:08,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Huh. Even tougher than the Toudou School?</b></font>

289
00:23:08,934 --> 00:23:11,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah. So it seems.</b></font>

290
00:23:11,004 --> 00:23:14,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I look forward to it, what kind of racer he'll be.</b></font>

291
00:23:14,804 --> 00:23:19,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I was just thinking I'd like to get
into a good, solid scuffle of a race.</b></font>

292
00:23:19,444 --> 00:23:24,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The Saitama area was pretty much
a string of small-time opponents.</b></font>

293
00:23:24,984 --> 00:23:29,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That being said, there were
some good moments for me.</b></font>

294
00:23:29,014 --> 00:23:32,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I was able to tackle some of my
assigned tasks at a leisurely pace.</b></font>

295
00:23:32,754 --> 00:23:36,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah. I guess we could
think of the Saitama area</b></font>

296
00:23:36,194 --> 00:23:41,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>as being a training stage for
you to improve your skills.</b></font>

297
00:23:41,364 --> 00:23:45,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>As I see it, there's no doubt
that you've gotten much better.</b></font>

298
00:23:45,664 --> 00:23:50,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I guess. Even I think I've come quite a ways.</b></font>

299
00:23:50,044 --> 00:23:56,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>To me, the expedition wasn't too exciting,
but it was rich in content. I won't forget it.</b></font>

300
00:23:56,944 --> 00:24:00,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I see. Then I'm glad.</b></font>

301
00:24:07,394 --> 00:24:10,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Say, Fumihiro...</b></font>

302
00:24:10,064 --> 00:24:15,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Do you think my brother calculates all
this when deciding where we go next?</b></font>

303
00:24:20,404 --> 00:24:22,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Probably.</b></font>

304
00:24:25,574 --> 00:24:30,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>All of Ryosuke's decisions
have a reason behind them.</b></font>

305
00:24:30,214 --> 00:24:34,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I wonder if, to my brother, Fujiwara
and I are still just babes-in-arms.</b></font>

306
00:24:34,584 --> 00:24:37,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't worry about that sort of thing.</b></font>

307
00:24:37,984 --> 00:24:39,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah...</b></font>

308
00:24:44,094 --> 00:24:49,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It can be vexing, but I've got myself
one heck of an older brother.</b></font>

309
00:24:51,034 --> 00:24:53,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Our next expedition will be Ibaraki, huh?</b></font>

310
00:24:53,874 --> 00:24:56,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yes. I've already taken a look.</b></font>

311
00:24:56,704 --> 00:24:59,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No matter who I face, I don't think I'll lose.</b></font>

312
00:24:59,674 --> 00:25:03,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>With this, I'll race so fast it'll
make my brother's head spin!</b></font>

313
00:25:21,194 --> 00:25:25,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Senjou ni saita rose,</i>
<i>for the reason they don't know</i></b></font>

314
00:25:25,204 --> 00:25:29,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Mae ni shika susumenai caterpillar</i>
<i>ga kyou mo fumitsubushita</i></b></font>

315
00:25:29,074 --> 00:25:33,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Yo, hates and pain, nikushimi dake fuyashite</i></b></font>

316
00:25:33,374 --> 00:25:37,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Hates and pain, sonna sesou, live eizou</i></b></font>

317
00:25:37,484 --> 00:25:46,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Dakishimete ite ne, motto tsuyoi te de</i></b></font>

318
00:25:46,224 --> 00:25:52,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Fuan na yoru ni anata no koe</i>
<i>(For the reason they don't know)</i></b></font>

319
00:25:52,394 --> 00:25:58,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Sekai wa itsuka chi o nagashite ite</i>
<i>(All around the world)</i></b></font>

320
00:25:58,464 --> 00:26:08,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Sonna news o wasuresasete yo, wakaritakunai</i></b></font>

321
00:26:09,584 --> 00:26:16,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Nobody reason, nobody sure where is the end</i></b></font>

322
00:26:16,624 --> 00:26:25,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Aa semete mou sukoshi,</i>
<i>uso demo ii, yasashiku utatte</i></b></font>

323
00:26:25,164 --> 00:26:29,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Sakusou suru jouhou wa</i>
<i>mass media-tachi ni mou hora</i></b></font>

324
00:26:29,164 --> 00:26:33,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Ressei ga noukou na</i>
<i>taikyoku no urei o tsutaedasu</i></b></font>

325
00:26:33,204 --> 00:26:37,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Risei wa kanensei,</i>
<i>yokushiryoku o kaiteru nenrei, yeah</i></b></font>

326
00:26:37,204 --> 00:26:41,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Dokomade senrei uketsuzukeru zenshin zenrei</i></b></font>

327
00:26:41,514 --> 00:26:48,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Nobody reason, nobody sure where is the end</i></b></font>

328
00:26:48,514 --> 00:26:57,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Tayorinai kowaresou na fune koideru nara</i></b></font>

329
